            "link": "https://www.benzinga.com/personal-finance/management/25/08/46812619/the-more-value-you-provide-the-more-money-you-can-earn-how-this-self-made-millionaire-employed-one-to-infinity-leverage-growing-her-net-worth",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-02 08:02:12",
            "source": "benzinga",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
